          "html": "<div style=\"--color-page-graphite:#0f172a;--color-body-slate:#475569;--color-subtle-gray:#334155;--color-link-ash:#64748b;--color-violet-signal:#8a53e1;--color-porcelain-white:#e5e7eb;--color-snowdrift:#f2f3f5;--color-divider-silver:#d1d5db;--font-greycliff:'Inter',sans-serif;--shadow-xl:rgba(30,41,59,0.15) 0px 25px 50px -12px;box-sizing:border-box;width:600px;background:#ffffff;padding:64px 48px 56px 48px;font-family:var(--font-greycliff);\"><style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');</style><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:40px;\"><svg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 28 28\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 2 L16.5 10.5 L25 8 L19.5 15 L25 22 L16.5 19.5 L14 28 L11.5 19.5 L3 22 L8.5 15 L3 8 L11.5 10.5 Z\" fill=\"#8a53e1\"/></svg><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-greycliff);font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-page-graphite);letter-spacing:-0.025em;\">Limitless</span></div><h1 style=\"font-family:var(--font-greycliff);font-size:60px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.11;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-page-graphite);margin:0 0 32px 0;padding:0;\">Limitless has been acquired by Meta</h1><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-greycliff);font-size:18px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-body-slate);margin:0;padding:0;\">I'm excited to share that Limitless has been acquired by Meta. I'm going to share why we joined forces, what this means for customers, and what comes next.</p></div>",
          "name": "Announcement Hero Heading",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-page-graphite:#0f172a;--color-body-slate:#475569;--color-subtle-gray:#334155;--color-link-ash:#64748b;--color-violet-signal:#8a53e1;--color-porcelain-white:#e5e7eb;--color-snowdrift:#f2f3f5;--color-divider-silver:#d1d5db;--font-greycliff:'Inter',sans-serif;--shadow-xl:rgba(30,41,59,0.15) 0px 25px 50px -12px;box-sizing:border-box;width:600px;background:#ffffff;padding:0 0 8px 0;font-family:var(--font-greycliff);\"><style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');</style><div style=\"background:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;padding:40px 48px;box-shadow:var(--shadow-xl);\"><h2 style=\"font-family:var(--font-greycliff);font-size:30px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.43;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-subtle-gray);margin:0 0 24px 0;padding:0;\">Message from Dan Siroker, Co-Founder &amp; CEO</h2><div style=\"width:100%;height:1px;background:var(--color-divider-silver);margin-bottom:24px;\"></div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-greycliff);font-size:18px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-body-slate);margin:0 0 20px 0;padding:0;\">I'm excited to share that Limitless has been acquired by Meta. I'm going to share why we joined forces, what this means for customers, and what comes next.</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-greycliff);font-size:18px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-body-slate);margin:0 0 20px 0;padding:0;\">First, why? When we started Limitless five years ago, the world was very different. AI was a pipe dream to many. Hardware startups were considered unfundable, and a business that did both AI and hardware would have been considered ludicrous.</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-greycliff);font-size:18px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-body-slate);margin:0 0 20px 0;padding:0;\">But today is different. The world has changed. We're no longer working on a weird fringe idea. We're building a future that now seems inevitable. We're not alone.</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-greycliff);font-size:18px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-body-slate);margin:0 0 20px 0;padding:0;\">What does this mean for existing customers? <strong style=\"font-weight:600;color:var(--color-page-graphite);\">Good news.</strong> We will continue to support existing Pendant customers for at least another year, but we'll no longer sell the Pendant to new customers. You'll no longer need to pay a subscription, and existing customers get the Unlimited Plan for free.</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-greycliff);font-size:18px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-body-slate);margin:0 0 24px 0;padding:0;\">We just launched a feature to make it easy to <strong style=\"font-weight:600;color:var(--color-page-graphite);\">export all of your data</strong>. And of course, if you want to <strong style=\"font-weight:600;color:var(--color-page-graphite);\">delete all of your data</strong>, that is also very easy to do within the app.</p><div style=\"width:100%;height:1px;background:var(--color-divider-silver);margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-greycliff);font-size:18px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-body-slate);margin:0;padding:0;\">Thanks,<br><span style=\"font-weight:600;color:var(--color-page-graphite);\">Dan Siroker</span><br><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:var(--color-link-ash);\">Co-Founder &amp; CEO, Limitless</span></p></div></div>",
          "name": "CEO Message Content Card",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-page-graphite:#0f172a;--color-body-slate:#475569;--color-subtle-gray:#334155;--color-link-ash:#64748b;--color-violet-signal:#8a53e1;--color-porcelain-white:#e5e7eb;--color-snowdrift:#f2f3f5;--color-divider-silver:#d1d5db;--font-greycliff:'Inter',sans-serif;--shadow-xl:rgba(30,41,59,0.15) 0px 25px 50px -12px;box-sizing:border-box;width:600px;background:#ffffff;padding:20px 32px;font-family:var(--font-greycliff);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-divider-silver);\"><style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap'); .nav-link{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:#475569;text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.15s;} .nav-link:hover{color:#0f172a;} .signin-btn{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:#475569;text-decoration:none;background:transparent;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:9999px;padding:8px 20px;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color 0.15s,color 0.15s;} .signin-btn:hover{border-color:#8a53e1;color:#8a53e1;}</style><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\"><svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 28 28\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 2 L16.5 10.5 L25 8 L19.5 15 L25 22 L16.5 19.5 L14 28 L11.5 19.5 L3 22 L8.5 15 L3 8 L11.5 10.5 Z\" fill=\"#8a53e1\"/></svg><span style=\"font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-page-graphite);letter-spacing:-0.025em;\">Limitless</span></div><nav style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:28px;\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-link\">Home</a><a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-link\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;\">Solutions<svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\" style=\"margin-top:1px;\"><path d=\"M2 4 L6 8 L10 4\" stroke=\"#475569\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></a><a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-link\">Privacy</a><a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-link\">Developers</a><a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-link\">About</a></nav><a href=\"#\" class=\"signin-btn\">Sign In</a></div></div>",
